		<title>14HOLIDAY RESORT - SALTCOATS</title>
		<content>  Saltcoats used to be an important    
 holiday resort for{Glaswegians}but    
 this trade has declined. Recently the 
 local council has tried to{revive}the 
 industry - the beach areas have been  
 cleaned up and the{Saltcoats harbour  
 area is being{re-developed.           
  Most tourists stay in small boarding 
 houses and{Sandylands caravan park.   
                                       
                                       
  The tourists make full use of the    
 towns' leisure facilities{( see pages 
{12 and 13 ).                          
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
